            class="block basis-0 flex-shrink flex-grow p-2 mx-auto lg:mx-0 text-center lg:text-left mb-5">
            <p class="text-lg text-[#c3c3c3]">
               <span class="text-freshmarket-primary">Fresh Market</span> posee una
               inmejorable distribución, cuenta con una amplia variedad de zonas
               y rubros para tu negocio: Productos de primera necesidad, área financiera,
               zonas tecnológicas, de moda, belleza, boutique y bisutería.
            </p>
            <div
               class="mt-5 flex justify-center lg:justify-normal flex-wrap gap-3">
               <a
                  href="https://s3.us-east-2.amazonaws.com/recorridosvirtuales.ic/RECORRIDO360+FRESH+MARKET/index.htm"
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="py-[.7rem] px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-freshmarket-primary to-[#3da837c0] hover:scale-105 focus:ring-green-950 focus:ring-offset-indigo-200 transition ease-in text-center text-base font-semibold shadow-md focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 rounded-full inline-flex items-center justify-center text-gray-50 gap-x-2 leading-7 hover:opacity-90"
                  data-astro-source-file="C:/laragon/www/landing-fresh-market/src/components/Cta.astro"
                  data-astro-source-loc="20:331">
                  Visita el recorrido virtual
                  <svg
                     xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                     width="24"
                     height="24"
                     viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                     fill="none"
                     stroke="currentColor"
                     stroke-width="2"
                     stroke-linecap="round"
                     stroke-linejoin="round"
                     class="icon icon-tabler icons-tabler-outline icon-tabler-view-360-number"
                     ><path stroke="none" d="M0 0h24v24H0z" fill="none"
                     ></path><path
                        d="M14 6a1 1 0 0 0 -1 -1h-2a1 1 0 0 0 -1 1v6a1 1 0 0 0 1 1h2a1 1 0 0 0 1 -1v-2a1 1 0 0 0 -1 -1h-3"
                     ></path><path
                        d="M3 5h2.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5 1.5v1a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 -1.5 1.5h-1.5h1.5a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 1.5 1.5v1a1.5 1.5 0 0 1 -1.5 1.5h-2.5"
